How this NOTICE was checked
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Automated search under appbench-1.4/ for lines matching
   copyright|license|public domain|GPL|redistribut|All rights|NO WARRANTY
   across Forth/VHDL/README/COPYING sources (CVS/OUTPUT skipped).
2. Manual open of each component's primary headers (gc.fs, brew.fs /
   COPYING / README, brainless README + brainless.fs, lexex per-file
   headers, cross/vmgen Gforth headers, fcp and cd16sim tops).
3. Confirmed absence of license keywords under fcp/ and cd16sim/ with a
   recursive case-insensitive search.
4. Confirmed GPL major version strings: benchgc/brew/lexex/sets.fth use
   "either version 2"; cross/vmgen use "either version 3".
